    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sink your teeth into a gothic Match-3 adventure in this ghoulish new installment of the Jewel Match series.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217090/extras/6f7b417e29eb33659063788a3e8eeee9.avif?t=1729877706\" width=600 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a powerful vampire lord, you'll tackle eerie match-3 puzzles to resurrect and refurbish the legendary Castle Dracula. Use mystical gem magic to unveil new castle elements, transforming dilapidated ruins into a grand fortress worthy of the Prince of Darkness himself. Venture through vast levels filled with mysterious treasures awaiting discovery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217090/extras/a62f2025639cb341593c0dd63b36d017.webp?t=1729877706\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in bonus mini-games, including hidden object scenes and puzzles, to gather resources for your sinister quest. Peruse an extensive collection of ghastly power-ups available in the nocturnal store. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217090/extras/f14a06fdbd6f92509a71be269bad4804.webp?t=1729877706\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you become the master architect of perpetual darkness, constructing the most feared castle in the realm? A thrilling journey into shadow beckons, dark lord. Carve your legacy into the realm of eternal night in this unique Match-3 experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217090/extras/93d46bea91ec6d33431b5feb18078034.webp?t=1729877706\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse 150 vast chambers of Castle Dracula! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through 40 additional cryptic levels, unveiling new challenges! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from three unique game modes: Timed, Relaxed and Limited Moves! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tailor your sinister quest with three difficulty levels: Normal, Advanced and Extreme. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resurrect a majestic gothic fortress, designing its shadowy halls and secret passages. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your vampiric powers by purchasing various upgrades and powerful boosts in the in-game store. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indulge in replayable mini-games featuring bewitching puzzles and captivating 'spot the difference' challenges.  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock haunting wallpapers for your desktop.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
